/p>\r\n', '\r\n<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Động cơ I6 , 6 xi lanh thẳng h&agrave;ng</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dung t&iacute;ch động cơ: 2.497 cc</strong></p>\r\n<p>C&ocirc;ng su&acirc;́t cực đại: 150(204) kw tại 6.100 v&ograve;ng ph&uacute;t</p>\r\n<p>M&ocirc;men xoắn cực đại: 250Nm tại 2750-3000 v&ograve;ng ph&uacute;t</p>\r\n<p>D&agrave;i x Rộng x Cao:&nbsp;<span style="font-size: x-small;">4899 x 2094 x 1464&nbsp;</span>mm</p>\r\n<p>Chiều d&agrave;i cơ sở: 2.968 mm</p>\r\n<p>V&acirc;̣n t&ocirc;́c t&ocirc;́i đa: 234 km/h</p>\r\n<p>Khả năng tăng tốc 0-100 km/h: 8.5 gi&acirc;y</p>\r\n<p>Ti&ecirc;u hao nhi&ecirc;n li&ecirc;̣u: 7.6&nbsp;l&iacute;t/ 100km</p>\r\n<p>Tự trọng: 1650 kg</p>\r\n', '2263000000', 'BMW', 1, NULL, 127, '840674666_oqa1295842402.jpg', 2, 0, 1, '2996cc', 'Sedan', '8 số tự động', '5'),
(38, 'BMW 535i GT', '\r\n<p>\r\n<object width="535" height="350" data="http://www.youtube.com/v/nfQaUK-Epn0" type="application/x-shockwave-flash">\r\n<param name="data" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/nfQaUK-Epn0" />\r\n<param name="src" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/nfQaUK-Epn0" />\r\n</object>\r\n</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p><span lang="VI"><a><img src="http://www.caranddriver.com/var/ezflow_site/storage/images/reviews/car/09q4/2010_bmw_5-series_gran_turismo_535i_gran_turismo-second_drive/gallery/2010_bmw_535i_gran_turismo_28euro_spec_29_photo_17/3033155-1-eng-US/2010_bmw_535i_gt_24_cd_gallery.jpg" alt="2010 BMW 535i Gran Turismo (Euro spec)" width="576" height="352" /></a></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="VI"><a><img src="http://www.caranddriver.com/var/ezflow_site/storage/images/reviews/car/09q4/2010_bmw_5-series_gran_turismo_535i_gran_turismo-second_drive/gallery/2010_bmw_535i_gran_turismo_28euro_spec_29_photo_18/3033169-1-eng-US/2010_bmw_535i_gt_25_cd_gallery.jpg" alt="2010 BMW 535i Gran Turismo (Euro spec)" width="576" height="352" /></a></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="VI"><a><img src="http://www.caranddriver.com/var/ezflow_site/storage/images/reviews/car/09q4/2010_bmw_5-series_gran_turismo_535i_gran_turismo-second_drive/gallery/2010_bmw_535i_gran_turismo_28euro_spec_29_photo_27/3033295-1-eng-US/2010_bmw_535i_gt_33_cd_gallery.jpg" alt="2010 BMW 535i Gran Turismo (Euro spec)" /></a></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="VI"><a><img src="http://www.caranddriver.com/var/ezflow_site/storage/images/reviews/car/09q4/2010_bmw_5-series_gran_turismo_535i_gran_turismo-second_drive/gallery/2010_bmw_535i_gran_turismo_28euro_spec_29_photo_22/3033225-1-eng-US/2010_bmw_535i_gt_29_cd_gallery.jpg" alt="2010 BMW 535i Gran Turismo (Euro spec)" /></a></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="VI"><a><img src="http://www.caranddriver.com/var/ezflow_site/storage/images/reviews/car/09q4/2010_bmw_5-series_gran_turismo_535i_gran_turismo-second_drive/gallery/2010_bmw_535i_gran_turismo_headlight_28euro_spec_29_photo_23/3